eleanor 's secret ( original french title kérity , la maison des contes ) is a 2009 franco-italian animated feature film directed by dominique monféry . it won the special distinction prize at the 2010 annecy international animated film festival . the film was produced in separate versions with french and english soundtracks . eleanor 's secret had a limited uk cinema showing and was released on dvd in 2011 by soda pictures . it had no general release in the united states , but was made available for individual bookings . it was later released direct-to-video on 12 august 2014 from cinedigm .